cst8284.asgmt4.roomScheduler

Class RoomBookingDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • cst8284.asgmt4.roomScheduler.RoomBookingDialog

  • public class RoomBookingDialog
extends java.lang.Object
    Class RoomBookingDialog is used to add / search / change / delete a room booking information. Customer could input the date and time to search the booking information at first, then change the time, or delete the booking. Built up in assignment 4.
    Version:
    1.04
    Author:
    Ye Zhang
